text:
What a journey these WAGS are on! In this first look at season three of WAGS L.A., Barbie Blank is already feeling the “trials and tribulations” of her first year of marriage to husband Sheldon Souray.

Read more: http://www.eonline.com/shows/wags/news/889591/barbie-blank-worries-husband-sheldon-souray-might-want-a-divorce-in-wags-l-a-season-3-first-look
title: Barbie Blank Worries Husband Sheldon Souray Might Want a “Divorce” in WAGS L.A. Season 3 First Look
